<div class="profile-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-header">
            <div class="profile-avatar">üë§</div>
            <div class="profile-info">
                <h1 id="displayName">Bienvenido, {{profile.allName}}</h1> 
                <p id="displayEmail">{{profile.email}}</p>
                <p id="displayUsername">@{{profile.userName}}</p>
                
                <div class="profile-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">{{videoCount}}</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Videos</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">{{monthsActive}}</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Meses Activo</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-section view-mode" id="personalInfo">
            <h2 class="section-title">Informaci√≥n Personal</h2>
            <form id="profileForm">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="allName">Nombre Completo</label>
                        <input type="text" id="allName" name="allName" value="{{profile.allName}}" readonly>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="userName">Nombre de Usuario</label>
                        <input type="text" id="userName" name="userName" value="{{profile.userName}}" readonly>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Correo Electr√≥nico</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" value="{{profile.email}}" readonly>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="age">Edad</label>
                        <input type="number" id="age" name="age" value="{{profile.age}}" readonly>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="btn-container">
                    <button type="button" class="btn-primary" id="editBtn">Editar Perfil</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-primary" id="saveBtn" style="display: none;">Guardar Cambios</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" id="cancelBtn" style="display: none;">Cancelar</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="profile-section danger-zone">
            <h2 class="section-title">Zona de Peligro</h2>
            <p>Una vez que eliminas tu cuenta, no hay vuelta atr√°s. Por favor, ten la seguridad de que deseas hacerlo.</p>
            <button type="button" class="btn-danger" id="deleteBtn">Eliminar mi cuenta permanentemente</button>
        </div>
        </div>
</div>

<script src="/js/profile.js" defer></script>